cdata.name: XDNA
cdata.desc:
XDNA is aPoW/PoS cryptocurrency that uses the Keccak algorithm.XDNA features a second layer network of masternodes that process private and near-instant transactions. It also has another feature named BitGun thataims to provide dynamic changed block rewards. In addition, a dual mining mode in Claymore's miner option is available to the user.

XDNA foundation is associated with XDNA and it is a non-commercial charity fund that aims to makes useof modern technologies to spread their donations around the world.
